headline.print_headline: Biden, Ukraine Leader Discuss Cease-Fire Efforts
headline.main: Biden, Ukraine Leader Discuss Cease-Fire Efforts

lead_paragraph: Ukrainian President Petro Poroshenko has told Vice President Joe Biden that Ukraine's offers for cease-fire talks were all rejected by either Russia or pro-Russian separatists.
